@fanli819 Yes, Germany’s leading ficonTEC is a 100% wholly owned Chinese subsidiary now. 

Because RoboTechnik over in Suzhou bought them for $260m… because the company lacked funding and Germany/EU wouldn’t support them with enough capital. 

So China is a large beneficiary of the photonics upside, and will likely do well now over in Shenzhen’s stock exchange.
